Package org.apache.struts2.util

Class SortIteratorFilter

java.lang.Object
org.apache.struts2.util.IteratorFilterSupport
org.apache.struts2.util.SortIteratorFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterator, Action
public class SortIteratorFilter extends IteratorFilterSupport implements Iterator, Action
A bean that takes a source and comparator then attempt to sort the source utilizing the comparator. It is being used in SortIteratorTag.
